Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:53.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}看不到終點的迷宮 被雨淋濕的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:57.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\3c&HF3912C&\blur1.5\bord1.5}雖然沒有什麼後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&HF3A42D&\blur1.5}叫喊的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:05.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,323)\3c&HF3A42D&\blur1.5}一定會傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:12.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}在宣告這個故事開始的鐘聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:16.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,250)\3c&HBF9D8F&\blur1.5}所連接的旅途之中
