Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:26.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H89B63F&\blur1.5}被指引到曾幾何時的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:31.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,80)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將兩份願望逐一化為有形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:35.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H5187D8&\blur1.5}將奇跡 不斷超越
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:40.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H44ACC3&\blur1.5}你所描繪的未來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:45.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,250)\3c&H4697D0&\blur1.5}現在也在哪裏存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:53.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,450)\3c&HE4772B&\blur1.5}將那無論承載多少夢想 絕無虛偽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,0)\3c&HB1601B&\blur1.5}Ah… Oh 一直做我自己
